headline.main: Cold Putter Prevents McIlroy From Challenging in Mexico
headline.print_headline: Cold Putter Prevents McIlroy From Challenging in Mexico

lead_paragraph: Rory McIlroy never looked like he would regain his world number one ranking on Sunday as a cold putter prevented him from mounting a challenge in the final round at the WGC-Mexico Championship.
